title: Philosophy The Microdelivery Exfoliating Wash 32 oz
description:
Why is it different: The microdelivery exfoliating wash is a mild daily scrub designed to effectively cleanse the skin while resurfacing. The unique, sulfate-free formula helps replenish and protect the skin, while topical antioxidants condition and moisturize.

How do I use it: Apply to a slightly damp face and massage for 30 to 40 seconds and rinse thoroughly. For the ultimate resurfacing treatment, use the microdelivery exfoliating wash in conjunction with philosophy's microdelivery exfoliating cloths one to two times per week.

title: CeraVe SPF 50 Sunscreen Face Lotion, 2 Ounce
description: CeraVe sunscreen, face lotion with SPF 50 with invisible zinc, which delivers its unique dry, clear finish for powerful protection from the sun's damaging rays. The patented MVE delivery technology ensures a slow, gradual release of these ingredients for all day hydration and comfort.
